Package: rllr
Type: Package
Title: What the Package Does (Title Case)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "James", "Curran",
      email = "j.curran@auckland.ac.nz",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: This package offers a set of functions for the evaluation and calibration of scoring (log-likelihood ratio
    ) systems, such as Cost of log-likelihood ratio (C_llr), Empirical Cross Entropy (ECE) Plots, and Detection Error
    Tradeoff (DET) curves.
